== prompt 2 :: unit=typescript-example/src/math.ts.multiply :: pass=summary ==
You are analyzing a TypeScript function to create a summary of its behavior.

```
export function multiply(a: number, b: number): number {
    let result = 0;
    for (let i = 0; i < b; i++) {
        result = add(result, a);
    }
    return result;
}
```

